ITEM 2.02. RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION On February 1, 2005, Anixter International Inc. (the "Company") reported its results for the fiscal quarter ended December 31, 2004. The Company's press release, dated February 1, 2005 is attached as Exhibit 99.1. ITEM 9.01. FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS (c) Exhibits 99.1 Press Release, dated February 1, 2005 issued by Anixter International Inc.
