Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
On October 24, 2006, Anixter International Inc. (the "Company") reported its results for the fiscal quarter ended September 29, 2006. The Companys press release, dated October 24, 2006, is attached as Exhibit 99.1.
Item 9.01 Financial Statements and Exhibits.
Exhibits 99.1 Press Release, dated October 24, 2006, issued by Anixter International Inc.
Top of the Form
Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned hereunto duly authorized.
