     (e) Notwithstanding the provisions of above, no Lender shall be required to purchase a participation interest in a British Pound Sterling Loan pursuant to this if, at least two Business Days prior to the making of such British Pound Sterling Loan, the Administrative Agent and the British Pound Sterling Lenders received written notice
