2.18 Increase in Commitments.
     (a) . Provided there exists no Default, upon notice to the Administrative Agent (which shall promptly notify the Lenders), Anixter may from time to time, request an increase in the Aggregate Commitments by an amount (for all such requests) not exceeding US$100,000,000; that (i) any such request for an increase shall be in a minimum amount of US$15,000,000, and (ii) Anixter may make a maximum of two such requests in any calendar year.
