(i) for the period from and after the date of this Agreement and prior to such Closing Date there has not occurred any Material Adverse Change;
(ii) the representations and warranties of the Company and the Guarantor set forth in Section 1 of this Agreement are true and correct on and as of such Closing Date with the same force and effect as though expressly made on and as of such Closing Date; and
