On July 9, 2012, Anixter International Inc. (the "Company") announced that it purchased Jorvex, S.A. on June 28, 2012 for approximately $56.2 million and assumed approximately $10.5 million in debt. The final purchase price will be subject to a net asset adjustment. For additional information, see the Companys Press Release dated July 9, 2012, which is attached as Exhibit 99.1.
